      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EQUIVOCAL (2) missed the frame latest (31.59) when fifth over 530m at Angle Park in a Grade 6. Rates a leading player. QUINCE BALE (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Bristol Moss (31.21) in a Grade 6. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Will give a great sight again. LEGS ELEVEN (4) is having her first start around this course. In the money last start when second (34.63) at Angle Park over 595m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Bold showing expected. ZINFANDEL DASH (5) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good recent form but could only manage second (19.74) at Angle Park. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Likely to be in the finish again.",
